com.cyc.baseclient.datatype

Class ContinuousTimeInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.datatype.AbstractTimeInterval
      • com.cyc.baseclient.datatype.ContinuousTimeInterval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimeInterval

    public class ContinuousTimeInterval
extends AbstractTimeInterval
    A Java representation of continuous time intervals.

    Continuous time intervals are defined in terms of a start and an end, and either include or do not include each endpoint.
